t and financial solutions. Commonwealth Bank of Australia was founded in 1911 and is based in Sydney, Australia.", "financialCurrency": "AUD", "totalRevenue": 28466999296, "grossProfits": 28466999296, "operatingIncome": null, "netIncomeToCommon": 10403000320, "country": "Australia"}, "currency": "AUD", "usd_rate": 0.7270084023475647}}